            "title": "[ΊΝΝΉζ┤ΉΞυ Ά╕░Ή┤Ι] 07. Numpy_broadcasting Ήζ┤ΊΧ┤ Έ░Π ΊβεΉγσΊΧαΆ╕░",
            "date_published": "2021-07-13T15:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>ΉΕεΈκε ΈΜνΈξ╕ Ή░ρΉδΡΉζα numpyΈΒ╝Έου ΉΩ░ΉΓ░ΊΧαΈΛΦ Έ░σΈ▓ΧΉζ╕ broadcastingΉζα Ά░εΈΖΡΉΩΡ ΈΝΑΊΧ┤ ΉΗΝΆ░εΊΧσΈΜΙΈΜν.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> numpy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> np</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ\">#</a> Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ά╕░Έ│╕ΉιΒΉε╝Έκε numpyΉζα ΉΩ░ΉΓ░ΉζΑ ShapeΉζ┤ Ά░βΉζΑ ΈΣΡ ndarrayΉΩΡ ΈΝΑΊΧε ΉΩ░ΉΓ░ΈπΝΉζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧαΈΜν.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ΊΧαΉπΑΈπΝ, ΉΕεΈκε ShapeΉζ┤ ΈΜνΈξ╕ numpyΈΒ╝ΈουΈΠΕ ΉΩ░ΉΓ░Ήζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧε Ά▓╜Ήγ░Ά░Α ΉηΙΈΜν. Ήζ┤Έξ╝ Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥε Ή║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ(ShapeΉζΕ ΈπηΉ╢ν)Ήζ┤Έζ╝ ΊΧεΈΜν.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ-rule\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ-rule\">#</a> Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ Rule</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/user/basics.broadcasting.html#general-broadcasting-rules\">Ά│╡ΉΜζΈυ╕ΉΕε</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ΈΤ╖ Ή░ρΉδΡΉΩΡΉΕε Έ╢ΑΊΕ░ Έ╣ΕΆ╡ΡΊΧαΉΩυ ShapeΉζ┤ Ά░βΆ▒░ΈΓα, Ή░ρΉδΡ ΉνΣ Ά░ΤΉζ┤ 1Ήζ╕ Ά▓ΔΉζ┤ Ήκ┤ΉηυΊΧαΈσ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξ</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.tutorialspoint.com/numpy/images/array.jpg\" alt=\"Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ ΉαΙ\" /></p>\n<pre><code>- Ή╢εΉ▓α: https://www.tutorialspoint.com/numpy/images/array.jpg \n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>ΉεΕΉζα Ά╖╕Έο╝ΉΩΡΉΕε 2Έ▓ΙΉπ╕ numpyΈΛΦ ΉΓυΉΜνΉΔΒ (1x3)Ήζ┤ΈΜν. =&gt; ΉοΚ, Ή░ρΉδΡ ΉνΣ Ά░ΤΉζ┤ 1Ήζ┤ ΉηΙΈΛΦ Ά▓╜Ήγ░ΉΩΡ ΊΧ┤ΈΜ╣</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ά╖╕ΈθυΈψΑΈκε Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥε Ή║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖ RuleΉζΕ ΈπΝΉκ▒ΊΧαΉΩυ ΉΩ░ΉΓ░Ήζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧ┤ΉπΕΈΜν.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"shapeΉζ┤-Ά░βΉζΑ-Ά▓╜Ήγ░Ήζα-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#shapeΉζ┤-Ά░βΉζΑ-Ά▓╜Ήγ░Ήζα-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\">#</a> ShapeΉζ┤ Ά░βΉζΑ Ά▓╜Ήγ░Ήζα ΉΩ░ΉΓ░</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">15</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reshape<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rand<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">15</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reshape<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"x:\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"y:\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>x:<br />\n[[ 0  1  2  3  4]<br />\n[ 5  6  7  8  9]<br />\n[10 11 12 13 14]]</p>\n<p>y:<br />\n[[0.09750476 0.03329158 0.4588553  0.41886341 0.88091397]<br />\n[0.05444735 0.49626685 0.07778171 0.71429232 0.0817233 ]<br />\n[0.6663016  0.07144051 0.39546019 0.573171   0.06219814]]</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># Ά░Β indexΆ░Α ΈπνΉ╣φΈΡαΈΛΦ Ά░ΤΈΥνΈΒ╝Έου ΈΞΦΊΧ┤ΉΕε ΈΠβΉζ╝ΊΧε shapeΉζα ΊΨΚΈιυΉζ┤ ΈΓαΉαρΈΜν.</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 0.09750476,  1.03329158,  2.4588553 ,  3.41886341,  4.88091397],<br />\n[ 5.05444735,  6.49626685,  7.07778171,  8.71429232,  9.0817233 ],<br />\n[10.6663016 , 11.07144051, 12.39546019, 13.573171  , 14.06219814]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> y</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[0.        , 0.03329158, 0.91771061, 1.25659024, 3.52365589],<br />\n[0.27223674, 2.97760112, 0.544472  , 5.71433857, 0.7355097 ],<br />\n[6.66301595, 0.78584561, 4.74552231, 7.45122304, 0.87077392]])</p>\n<h3 id=\"scalarΉΔΒΉΙαΉβΑΉζα-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#scalarΉΔΒΉΙαΉβΑΉζα-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\">#</a> Scalar(ΉΔΒΉΙα)ΉβΑΉζα ΉΩ░ΉΓ░</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># ΉΔΒΉΙαΈΛΦ ΉΨ┤ΈΨιΊΧε shapeΉζα numpyΈζ╝ΈΠΕ ΉΩ░ΉΓ░Ήζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξ</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 2,  3,  4,  5,  6],<br />\n[ 7,  8,  9, 10, 11],<br />\n[12, 13, 14, 15, 16]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 0,  2,  4,  6,  8],<br />\n[10, 12, 14, 16, 18],<br />\n[20, 22, 24, 26, 28]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">**</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[  0,   1,   4,   9,  16],<br />\n[ 25,  36,  49,  64,  81],<br />\n[100, 121, 144, 169, 196]], dtype=int32)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ True, False,  True, False,  True],<br />\n[False,  True, False,  True, False],<br />\n[ True, False,  True, False,  True]])</p>\n<h1 id=\"shapeΉζ┤-ΈΜνΈξ╕-Ά▓╜Ήγ░-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#shapeΉζ┤-ΈΜνΈξ╕-Ά▓╜Ήγ░-ΉΩ░ΉΓ░\">#</a> ShapeΉζ┤ ΈΜνΈξ╕ Ά▓╜Ήγ░ ΉΩ░ΉΓ░</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reshape<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 4ΊΨΚ 3ΉΩ┤</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"aΈΛΦ\\n:\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">103</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bΈΛΦ\\n:\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><dl>\n<dt>aΈΛΦ</dt>\n<dd>[[ 0  1  2]<br />\n[ 3  4  5]<br />\n[ 6  7  8]<br />\n[ 9 10 11]]</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (4, 3)</p>\n<dl>\n<dt>bΈΛΦ</dt>\n<dd>[100 101 102]</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>bΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (3,)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>a <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> b</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[100, 102, 104],<br />\n[103, 105, 107],<br />\n[106, 108, 110],<br />\n[109, 111, 113]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1004</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cΈΛΦ\\n:\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reshape<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dΈΛΦ\\n:\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><dl>\n<dt>cΈΛΦ</dt>\n<dd>[1000 1001 1002 1003]</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>cΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (4,)</p>\n<dl>\n<dt>dΈΛΦ</dt>\n<dd>[[100 101 102]]</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>dΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (1, 3)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>a <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> c</pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (4, 3)</p>\n<p>cΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (4,)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>aΉβΑ cΉζα shapeΈξ╝ Έ│┤Έσ┤ ΈΣαΈΜν ΉΧηΉ░ρΉδΡΉζ┤ 4 Έ░░ΉΩ┤ΉζΕ Ά░ΨΆ│ι ΉηΙΉΨ┤ Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥεΉ║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖΉζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧι Ά▓Δ Ή▓αΈθ╝ Έ│┤Ήζ╕ΈΜν.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ΊΧαΉπΑΈπΝ Έ╕ΝΈκεΈΥε Ή║ΡΉΛνΊΝΖΉζΑ <strong>ΈΤν Ή░ρΉδΡΈ╢ΑΊΕ░ Έ╣ΕΆ╡Ρ</strong> Έξ╝ ΊΧαΆ╕░ ΈΧΝΈυ╕ΉΩΡ ΉΩΡΈθυΆ░Α Έ░εΉΔζΊΧαΈΛΦ Ά▓Δ</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>a <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> d</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[100, 102, 104],<br />\n[103, 105, 107],<br />\n[106, 108, 110],<br />\n[109, 111, 113]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dΉζα shapeΈΛΦ :\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shape<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>aΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (4, 3)</p>\n<p>dΉζα shapeΈΛΦ : (1, 3)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>ΈΠβΉζ╝ΊΧε Ήζ┤ΉειΈκε aΉβΑ dΈΛΦ ΈΤνΉς╜ Ή░ρΉδΡΉζ┤ ΈΠβΉζ╝ΊΧε shapeΉζ┤Ά╕░ ΈΧΝΈυ╕ΉΩΡ ΉΩ░ΉΓ░Ήζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧαΈΜν. (bΆ░Α ΉΩ░ΉΓ░Ήζ┤ Ά░ΑΈΛξΊΧε Ήζ┤ΉειΉβΑ ΈΠβΉζ╝)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>dΉζα Ά▓╜Ήγ░ Ή░ρΉδΡΆ░ΤΉζ┤ 1Ήζ╕ Ά▓ΔΉζ┤ ΈΥνΉΨ┤ ΉηΙΉε╝ΈψΑΈκε Ά░ΑΈΛξ</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
